Many changes, especially at the genus-level, have been recently made in the systematics of Scydmaeninae , and an annotated catalogue, including extinct taxa and complete synonymy and bibliography, will be published elsewhere. Below a list of valid supertribal, tribal and generic names is given, to incorporate the most recent synonymization of Cyrtoscydmini (
Newton 2015
) and Plaumanniolini (the present study) with Glandulariini.
